room_title: Escape room "The Lost Soul" by LOK'd Room Escape in Manchester
room_address: 750 E. Industrial Park Dr. Suite B Manchester, NH 03109
room_description: Many years ago Margaret Jones vanished without a trace. The spirit of her late husband (Alistair) haunts the couple’s study. Unable to rest until he knows the truth of her disappearance, Alistair’s curses all who enter. He’s desperately seeking your help to figure out what happened to her. Can you help this Lost Soul find peace?
